definition: easy/amiable/to change/to exchange/prefix corresponding to the English adjective suffix "-able" or "-ible"
surname Yi/abbr. for 易經|易经[Yi4 jing1], the Book of Changes

sentences.english: Cleaned out the garage and sold 2 old dehumidifiers on eBay.
sentences.chinese: 收拾了车库，在易趣上卖掉了两台旧除湿机。

sentences.english: eBay has consistently had one of the ugliest websites on the internet.
sentences.chinese: 易趣网依旧一如既往的丑。

sentences.english: If you sell a product, you can also list it on eBay.
sentences.chinese: 如果你卖一件产品，你也可以在易趣上展出来。

sentences.english: The reporter is searched in easy interesting net " acting practice " , the information that jumps out does not issue 100.
sentences.chinese: 记者在易趣网搜索“代练”，跳出的信息不下百条。

sentences.english: Ebays sales of holiday sweaters are 24% ahead of last year.
sentences.chinese: 易趣网站的节日毛衫销售量也比去年增加了24%。

sentences.english: And i've posted it to my pages and contacted e-bay about it.
sentences.chinese: 我已把这些信息发到我的网页上并和易趣取得了联系。

sentences.english: Ebay's sales of holiday sweaters are 24% ahead of last year.

sentences.english: What do you think of eBay-Eachnet's product search engine on the website?

sentences.english: Images are hosted on separate servers therefore you don t need to upload them to eBay.
sentences.chinese: 图片单独的服务器上托管，因此你不须上传到易趣。

sentences.english: I was really inspired by Freecycle, Craigslist, and of course eBay.
sentences.chinese: 我深受免费回收网，克雷格网和易趣网的启发。

sentences.english: Even older models of phone will have faceplates available on eBay.
sentences.chinese: 即使是较旧型号的手机将面板上提供的易趣。

sentences.english: I want someone to collect ebay's past 30days of Japanese buyer date.
sentences.chinese: 我希望有人来收集日本买家当日易趣过去的30天。

sentences.english: She bought a snack-sized baggie full from eBay for about $5.
sentences.chinese: 她花了大约5美元从易趣网买了一个点心大小的袋子。

sentences.english: Stick it up on eBay and auction it off.
sentences.chinese: 把它的图片贴到易趣网上，然后拍卖出去。

sentences.english: If eBay is your weakness, don't log on.
sentences.chinese: 如果易趣网购是你的弱点，不要上线。
